## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the potential biases of the sources. Some sources may have inherent biases based on their organizational missions or political affiliations. Additionally, the legal and ethical landscape surrounding capital punishment is continually evolving, which may affect the relevance of the findings over time. Further research and updated data are recommended for a more comprehensive analysis.